lume deterioration","evidence":"The lesson gives no fixed threshold; review the displayed OHLCV evidence manually.","value":null},{"status":"unknown","label":"Earnings risk","evidence":"Verified earnings date unavailable.","value":null}]},"sellIntoStrength":{"courseUse":"Late-stage market or stock: consider realizing gains into strength and resistance.","levels":{"oneR":185.57,"twoR":254.39,"threeR":323.21,"chartResistance":"unknown"},"climaxSignals":[{"status":"fail","label":"Correction volume exceeds every post-breakout day","evidence":"This signal is not present in the latest session.","value":false},{"status":"unknown","label":"Unusually high volume without matching price progress","evidence":"No verified event/chart judgement supplied.","value":null},{"status":"fail","label":"Longest daily candle since breakout","evidence":"Latest candle is not the widest since breakout.","value":false}],"positiveNewsNegativeReaction":{"status":"unknown","label":"Positive news with negative price action","evidence":"No verified news-reaction evidence supplied.","value":null}},"notes":["Technical stop is wider than 10%; this model entry is not feasible and no position size is suggested.","Verified earnings date unavailable; earnings risk remains Unknown."]},"mentions":[{"mentioned_at":"2026-06-16T10:00:19.000Z","text":"Serenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\n4h\nYeah... I'm not quite sure why everyone likes just throwing personal accusations.\n\nLike \"scam\" or  \"memestock\" every time I post a thesis. \n\nLike when I bought \n$AXTI\n (still holding shares btw):\n\n- spent the time mapping the InP substrate supply chain\n- found analyst sources\nShow more\nQuote\nLuminara Stocks\n@_stockResearch\n·\n6h\nReplying to @aleabitoreddit\n$AXTI  was a generational find brother. I remember you talked about it when it was around $17 or so and then there were a lot of doubters, especially in WSB BETS who named you “exit strategy “. Then the results came out and it crashed to $11. \nThat’s when I picked up a bunch to\n250\n43\n995\n233K","source":"browser_visible","url":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2066823176785457323"},{"mentioned_at":"2026-06-16T07:28:51.000Z","text":"Serenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\n7h\nFun throwback to random ideas back in 2025.\n\nBack then, \n$AAOI\n was $2B MC, \n$LITE\n was a $26B MC, \n$AXTI\n was $500M\n\nNow:\n- AAOI is $15.37B\n- Lumentum is $74.47B\n- AXT is $7.24B\n\nWas working off less information back then, given it was an early theme. \n\nObviously nuances with ASIC\nShow more\nQuote\nSerenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\nDec 22, 2025\nReplying to @manukafirth\n\"Late\". \n\n$LITE is a $26B MC in the center of every future $GOOGL TPU deployment, $NVDA/ $AMZN / other GPU/ASICs. \n\n8-12% BOM share of every Google TPU v7. This is like saying $NVDA was \"late\" when price it was a $1T MC.\n\nBut if you want want another player, $AAOI. \n\n$MSFT is\n187\n53\n933\n291K","source":"browser_visible","url":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2066785056031670657"},{"mentioned_at":"2026-06-13T12:53:13.000Z","text":"Serenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\n10h\nIt’s been officially 3 months since I posted my $SIVE long thesis back at 4 SEK.\n\nThis idea is now up ~1900%… \n\nWith many US institutions from JPM to Fidelity only recently entering positions.\n\nProbably my 2nd greatest thesis of all time after \n$AXTI\n.\n\nDid you listen anon?\nQuote\nSerenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\nMar 16\nSubscribers only\nSubscribe to unlock\n251\n63\n1.2K\n225K","source":"browser_visible","url":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2065779524248510758"},{"mentioned_at":"2026-06-13T04:20:16.000Z","text":"Serenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\n6h\nThe AI supremacy Wars begins.\n\nThink a lot of the upstream supply chain bottlenecks caused by each Country export controlling each other (eg. \n$AXTI\n)\n\nShould present some interesting opportunities in the near future.\n\nThat being said, Anthropic was getting distilled left and right\nShow more\nQuote\nAnthropic\n@AnthropicAI\n·\n10h\nThe US government, citing national security authorities, has issued an export control directive to suspend all access to Fable 5 and Mythos 5 by any foreign national, whether inside or outside the United States, including foreign national Anthropic employees.\n\nThe net effect of\n236\n119\n1.3K\n407K","source":"browser_visible","url":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2065650434644304165"}],"topDownContext":{"alignment":"Unknown","chains":[]}},{"symbol":"ALRIB","mention_count":2,"first_mention":"2026-06-15T14:56:05.000Z","latest_mention":"2026-06-18T07:43:15.000Z","mentions_24h":0,"tweets_24h":0,"prices":[],"last_close":null,"last_price_date":null,"new_24h":false,"lesson3":{"schemaVersion":"course_rules_v1","symbol":"ALRIB","availability":"unavailable","overallStatus":"unavailable","overallLabel":"Unavailable","reasons":["No valid OHLCV history."],"stage2":{"checks":[]},"pattern":{"confirmation":"unknown","candidates":[]},"pivot":null,"entryMethods":[],"screeningEvidence":[{"status":"unknown","label":"Sales growth","evidence":"No SEC U.S. issuer match for this symbol.","value":null},{"status":"unknown","label":"EPS growth","evidence":"No SEC U.S. issuer match for this symbol.","value":null},{"status":"unknown","label":"Industry strength","evidence":"No SEC U.S. issuer match for this symbol.","value":null},{"status":"pass","label":"Stock story reviewed","evidence":"A source account post with narrative context was reviewed. This confirms story review coverage, not thesis validity.","value":{"mentionTime":"2026-06-18T07:43:15.000Z","excerptLength":647},"sourceUrl":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2067513458812473533","sourceLabel":"Source account post","asOf":"2026-06-18T07:43:15.000Z"}]},"lesson4ModelPlan":{"schemaVersion":"course_rules_v1","kind":"model_plan","availability":"unavailable","disclaimer":"Model plan only; not an actual holding, live alert or order.","reason":"A candidate pivot and valid OHLCV are required."},"mentions":[{"mentioned_at":"2026-06-18T07:43:15.000Z","text":"Serenity @aleabitoreddit · 6h $ALRIB general meeting notes came out today. -2nd ROSIE System expected to be delivered shortly to a leading quantum computing player” in the US. - They’re also intensifying BD for their products used for BTO/STO on photonics and recorded strong interest. Just for background, Show more Quote Serenity @aleabitoreddit · Apr 9 $MSFT looks like a secret buyer of Riber < $ALRIB > for Microsoft Quantum. The broader market and algorithms likely don’t know this connection yet. MBEs are important for quantum computing, quantum dot lasers, VCSELs, and silicon photonics. But the long-term implications are 132 35 511 235K","source":"browser_visible","url":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2067513458812473533"},{"mentioned_at":"2026-06-15T14:56:05.000Z","text":"Serenity\n@aleabitoreddit\n·\n23h\nJust as a recap, these were all my core European longs:\n\n1. $SIVE\n2. $LPK\n3. $SOI\n4. $RPI \n5. $IQE\n6. $ALRIB\n7. $XFAB\n\nSivers: As you know by now, core laser chokepoint over next generation photonics, from 1.6T pluggables to CPO.\n\nEmbedded in many hyperscaler suppliers from Jabil\nShow more\nQuote\nDominik Gabovic\n@domiliebtgabi14\n·\nJun 15\nReplying to @aleabitoreddit\nDo you have some similar older stock picks, you still believe in and want for them to rise accordingly?\n267\n308\n2.3K\n625K","source":"browser_visible","url":"https://x.com/aleabitoreddit/status/2066535221554733278"}],"topDownContext":{"alignment":"Unknown","chains":[]}},{"symbol":"IQE","mention_count":1,"first_mention":"2026-06-15T14:56:05.000Z","latest_mention":"2026-06-15T14:56:05.000Z","mentions_24h":0,"tweets_24h":0,"prices":[],"last_close":null,"last_price_date":null,"new_24h":false,"lesson3":{"schemaVersion":"course_rules_v1","symbol":"IQE","availability":"unavailable","overallStatus":"unavailable","overallLabel":"Unavailable","reasons":["No valid OHLCV history."],"stage2":{"checks":[]},"pattern":{"confirmation":"unknown","candidates":[